title: Prep Football: Breaking down districts for area teams
text:
Share 
District play in football begins tonight and Tony Hawley and Tom Rackers talk about the opening round of games for area teams in all six classes in the podcast posted below. 
Teams discussed include the Jefferson City Jays, Helias Crusaders, Blair Oaks Falcons, California Pintos, Eldon Mustangs, School of the Osage Indians, Versailles Tigers, Fulton Hornets, South Callaway Bulldogs, North Callaway Thunderbirds, Southern Boone Eagles, Tipton Cardinals and Camdenton Lakers.
